description:
This is a 5 minute workout called '5 Minute Morning Yoga to Energize and Remove Sleepiness' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a short 5 minute movement yoga class to energize and get you ready for a great day.
